metadata.name: Moon Witch #1
metadata.description:
Moon Witch

Shine among the gray trunks, in the tangle of branches, in the lake of flowers. Illuminated by light, betrothed to darkness. Hold the pale light of the crescent of Moon goddess in your fragile palms. For your way lies on a thorny path, your way runs through voices... Dissecting the darkness, finding your shadow, hold the crescent moon, and do not let go forever...

Self-portrait.
May 2022.

3508x5382 px
